      <scopecontent id="aspace_05bc7e875ee3c1f5bb7bc6767fca4b24">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The materials consist of photographic prints from the scrapbook of Frederick Ely Williamson, Yale College Class of 1898. Includes images of individual students, student rooms and Yale buildings.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
